sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as Trust
    participant Docker as DockerManager
    participant Container as CaddyContainer
    participant Keychain as macOSKeychain

    User->>CLI: orbit trust
    CLI->>Docker: isRunning orbit-caddy
    alt not running
        CLI-->>User: error
    end
    CLI->>Container: cat root.crt to temp file
    Container-->>CLI: certificate
    CLI->>Keychain: sudo security add-trusted-cert
    Keychain-->>CLI: result
    CLI->>CLI: cleanup temp file
    CLI-->>User: success - restart browser
